{"tid":1201674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要有一首鼓動人心既示威歌","createTime":"2019-06-11T05:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:38:41.000Z","uid":7718,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0c97eb7a8f64c9f6d04964ee06d9a0c0d62436","tid":1201674,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"如果大家聽厭民陣唱膠歌，有冇諗過唱一首蓋過大台既歌呢？<br />\n<br />\n假設一下，學術討論。古代行軍打仗，士氣最為重要，當中軍樂正是鼓動人心。小弟思前想後，假設如果香港聽日成班人唱do you hear the people sing，會唔會有效提升士氣同埋識別友方？大家可以學術討論一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=TvR3yw6bni8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTvR3yw6bni8&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=03574344\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=TvR3yw6bni8</a>"},{"pid":"eed41158733392ebdc58e5b9b100b4a546922cde","tid":1201674,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3255ee05807bc5b7013d5ae800fc32186b2e7fc5","tid":1201674,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2fe720d12619ca6eb7ce399785374a5f8afd2d","tid":1201674,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a460376765628e8b78f4f8da47609a3f6cf787","tid":1201674,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f13edb2d53be19627bb89d948fc3d61302eb730","tid":1201674,"uid":258327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"美國國歌<img src=\"/a